Paper: hep-th/9807236

Date: 1998-07-30

Title: Expectation values of descendent fields in the sine-Gordon model

Authors: V.Fateev, D.Fradkin, S.Lukyanov, A.Zamolodchikov, Al.Zamolodchikov

Comments: 26 pages, 2 figures, harvmac TeX

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B540 (1999) 587-609

We obtain exactly the vacuum expectation values $<(\partial\phi)^2({\bar\partial}\phi) e^{i\alpha\phi}>$ in the sine-Gordon model and$<L_{-2}{\bar L}_{-2} \Phi_{l,k}>$ in $\Phi_{1,3}$ perturbed minimal CFT. Wediscuss applications of these results to short-distance expansions of two-pointcorrelation functions.